; --- Hand on the gun ---
; A primitive right hand visible holding the grip. Positions are approximate
; for the Quaternius gun GLBs (origin at grip, barrel along -Z after the
; -90 Y rotation). The hand sits behind the gun toward the camera so it
; reads as "the player is gripping this." Pure primitives — not a rigged
; FPS hand. Iterate when a real rigged hand asset lands.
[node name="Hand" type="Node3D" parent="."]

; Forearm sleeve (military fatigue green) extending toward camera.
[node name="Forearm" type="MeshInstance3D" parent="Hand"]
transform = Transform3D(1, 0, 0, 0, 1, 0, 0, 0, 1, -0.005, -0.06, 0.10)
mesh = SubResource("BoxMesh_forearm")
surface_material_override/0 = SubResource("Mat_sleeve")

